10 直到非常穩定"},{"pid":"f99ab381081bef49ad81b12ca2eabb6cfd3cb2b9","tid":1308254,"uid":271109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:01:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e18f0e50aaf69c6eea26f490cf1a121b7bfa0530","tid":1308254,"uid":138802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:44:17.000Z","msg":"食完a酸3個月<br />\n宜家開始係咁生了...<br />\n<br />\n真係好唔開心...諗緊食多次a酸 (但好似有人話唔得)/食zinc/食中藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7654f9ecf1e9c0e52581ac078067bc58762099ef","tid":1308254,"uid":67208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e18f0e50aaf69c6eea26f490cf1a121b7bfa0530","tid":1308254,"uid":138802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:44:17.000Z","msg":"食完a酸3個月<br />\n宜家開始係咁生了...<br />\n<br />\n真係好唔開心...諗緊食多次a酸 (但好似有人話唔得)/食zinc/食中藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:32:33.000Z","msg":"我食緊第2次<br />\n自己買藥"},{"pid":"f9dabdbb89fa86f634131517ed3ff2bfe270a4fd","tid":1308254,"uid":138802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7654f9ecf1e9c0e52581ac078067bc58762099ef","tid":1308254,"uid":67208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"qu